				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p205184">Re: Object data storing schemes -- as opposed to background</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=205184#p205184"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Mon Sep 25, 2017 10:39 am&nbsp;</div></td>
